  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Admin cum Account Assistant",
  "description": "<p>Administrative Role: Operations Support</p><p></p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><p>1. Manage daily verification and data input into DO software</p><p>2. Monitor WhatsApp photo updates to ensure tasks are completed and recorded in DO software</p><p>3. Coordinate with ground staff for smooth operations</p><p>4. Escalate complex issues to support team and follow up via WhatsApp</p><p>5. Monitor Road Tax prerequisites and renew online</p><p>6. Coordinate vehicle inspections with customers (Rental)</p><p>7. Process VPC and insurance applications</p><p>8. Update fleet records (Rental/Road Tax) and inspection records in Excel</p><p>9. File vehicle quotations, customer orders, and inspection certificates (Owned)</p><p>10. Notify customers of vehicle return via WhatsApp</p><p>11. Issue work order books and papers for repairs/tyres (JIC/STA)</p><p>12. Assist Accounts Department with invoice preparation</p><p>13. Perform other tasks as assigned</p><p></p><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><p>- O Level or above</p><p>- Preferably with 2 years of working experience</p><p>- Basic MS Office (Excel, Word) skills</p><p>- Team player with good communication and problem-solving skills</p><p>- Able to work effectively in high-pressure environments</p>",
